#

Spicy Grilled Salmon with Avocado Salsa

25 min
$15
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

AmericanMexican

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

HealthyQuickGrilled

Description

A zesty, spicy salmon fillet topped with creamy avocado salsa, perfect for a quick and healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • avocado: 1, diced
  • tomato: 1, diced
  • red onion: 1/4, finely chopped
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
